snippet.title: Andy Samberg Got Emotional Filming Brooklyn Nine-Nine’s Final Season
snippet.description:
Andy Samberg talks about fighting a cold, returning one of Seth’s holiday cards and filming the eighth season of his show Brooklyn Nine-Nine.
